Raymond Griffith https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Raymond_Griffith 0 Raymond Griffith (January 23, 1895 – November 25, 1957) was a silent movie comedian. Later in his career, he worked behind the camera as writer and producer. Raymond_Griffith ( January_23_,_1895 – November_25_,_1957 ) was a_silent_movie_comedian .
